metadata.name: re-fracture001
metadata.description:
Due to complete insanity of Rogozin (Russias Space Agency Director) with threats of danger of dissolution of ISS and in not so distant future the complete demolition of the space station by crashing it into the Pacific ocean manifests the end of an Era that united astronauts and cosmonauts from around the world. 

I am purposefully wearing Pink Glasses to reverse time-space, to regenerate, to rebuild. 
[part 1]
